====================================
X-I-A Meta
====================================

A straight-forward definition of all creature in the XIA-meta.

There are two basic notion:

* Worker: Information holder
* Provisioner: Service provider

Worker is "alive" only when supported by a provisioner. Unlike worker, provisioner should hold only cached information.

* Connector: a special component of provisioner to communicate with other Worker (defined or undefined in XIA-Meta)

Quick start
=============================

Install the package::

    pip install xia-meta




